Command to run mavros
ros2 run mavros mavros_node --ros-args -p fcu_url:="udp://127.0.0.1:14550@" -p gcs_url:="udp://@127.0.0.1:14551" -p system_id:=255


Command to run arduSub
cd ~/ardupilot/ArduSub
sim_vehicle.py -v ArduSub -f vectored_6dof --model JSON -L RATBeach \
    --out=udp:0.0.0.0:14550 --console

Command to start gazebo
 cd ~/hydronaut_ws
export GZ_SIM_RESOURCE_PATH=~/hydronaut_ws/src/hydronaut_description/models
export GZ_SIM_RESOURCE_PATH=~/hydronaut_ws/src/hydronaut_description/models:~/hydronaut_ws/src/hydronaut_pilot/models:$GZ_SIM_RESOURCE_PATH

gz sim ~/hydronaut_ws/src/hydronaut_description/worlds/hydronaut_ocean.sdf -r



To run the script
cd ~/hydronaut_ws
cd scripts
python3 alt_hold_driver.py


